    <h1>About Awareness VR</h1>
    <p class="p-2">Thanks for visiting! Awarness VR is a project dedicated to bringing easy-to-learn vr meditation exercises to low-income youth in the UK. 34% of children in the UK live under the poverty line, leading to significant, lifelong challenges related to mental health. Meditation pracitce is proven to ameliorate mental health issues among youth, though it continues to be a challenge for youth to learn it and apply the practice to their lives. Awareness VR aims to make this easier by offering immersive meditation trainings trailored to their needs. </p>


